{"prompt": "Build a website for a children's book author. The theme should be whimsical and incorporate a playful yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Whimsical Children's Book Author</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Comic Sans MS', cursive, sans-serif;\n            background-color: #FFFACD; /* Playful yellow */\n            color: #333;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            min-height: 100vh;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .container {\n            background-color: #FFEFD5; /* A softer, complementary yellow */\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 15px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin: 20px;\n        }\n        h1 {\n            color: #FFD700; /* A slightly richer yellow */\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: #FFA500; /* Orange-yellow */\n            margin-top: 25px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n        }\n        p {\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n        .book-list img {\n            width: 150px;\n            height: 200px;\n            margin: 15px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            border: 3px solid #FFD700;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .book-list img:hover {\n            transform: scale(1.05);\n        }\n        .contact-form {\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            background-color: #FFF8DC; /* Cornsilk, another soft yellow */\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            border: 2px dashed #FFD700;\n        }\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid #FFD700;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-family: 'Comic Sans MS', cursive, sans-serif;\n        }\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: #FFD700;\n            color: #FFFACD;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 20px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #FFA500;\n        }\n        footer {\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            color: #8B4513; /* Saddle brown for contrast */\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h1>Welcome to the Magical World of [Author Name]!</h1>\n        <p>\n            Embark on an enchanting journey through stories filled with wonder, laughter, and a sprinkle of stardust. Perfect for little dreamers and curious minds!\n        </p>\n\n        <h2>My Latest Adventures</h2>\n        <div class=\"book-list\">\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/150/FFD700/333?text=Book+1\" alt=\"Book Cover 1\">\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/150/FFA500/333?text=Book+2\" alt=\"Book Cover 2\">\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/150/FFFACD/333?text=Book+3\" alt=\"Book Cover 3\">\n        </div>\n\n        <h2>About the Author</h2>\n        <p>\n            [Author Name] believes that every child has a universe inside them waiting to be discovered. With a passion for imagination and a heart full of stories, I craft tales that aim to inspire, delight, and encourage little readers to explore their own creativity.\n        </p>\n\n        <h2>Let's Connect!</h2>\n        <div class=\"contact-form\">\n            <p>Have a question, a book idea, or just want to say hello? Send me a message!</p>\n            <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Your Name\">\n            <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\">\n            <textarea placeholder=\"Your Message\" rows=\"4\"></textarea>\n            <button>Send Message</button>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <footer>\n        &copy; 2023 [Author Name]. All rights reserved.\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"}